  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Add</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Autoscaling monthly reports</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Improvements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Design improvements on Custom Domains component</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span>Bugs</span></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>VPN was sticking when trying to connect when provided with incorrect info</li>\n<li>In General Activities, the AutoScaling activity was not being shown</li>\n<li>There were no email and alerts showing the service had scaled via AutoScaling</li>\n<li>After deleting a service, there was no indication to the user that it has been deleted</li>\n</ul>"
      },
